## General info

This project is portfolio site for Victor Tsay.

## Technologies

Project is created with:

- gastby version: 2.3.5
- react version: 16.8.6
- styled-components version: 4.3.2
- material-ui version: 4.2.1

## Setup

To run this project, install it locally using npm:

```
$ cd ../vt0826.github.io/
$ npm install
$ gastby develop
```
